item.title: Server creation help
item.dc:creator: @The_Guardian The Guardian
item.description:
@The_Guardian wrote:

Go to the downloads section and download a source. Get JDK, most of your content coding will be in client.java, so if you want to change the name, for example, you would edit it, then click compile, then if there are no errors, click run.
